lead_paragraph: The woman, 18, was walking with her father on Thursday night in Brooklyn when they were attacked by a group of men with a gun, the police said.

headline.main: Woman Raped by 5 Men in Brooklyn Playground, Police Say
headline.print_headline: Woman Raped by 5 Men in a Park, Police Say

abstract: Young woman is raped by five men in Brownsville, Brooklyn, park; woman's father had run for help after one of men, who was wielding gun, ordered him to leave.
